  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK281">
<l>eḷḷāmai vēṇṭuvā ṉeṉpā ṉeṉaittoṉṟuṅ</l>
<l>kaḷḷāmai kākkataṉ ṉeñcu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let him, who desires not to be despised, keep his mind from (the desire of) defrauding another of the smallest thing.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
